---
layout: "base"
title: "Handout-Drafts | PUK Zürich"
description: "Arbeitsstand und Voransichten für neu aufzubauende Handouts."
useSharedCSS: true
useNavJS: false
---
{% block headCSS %}
<style>
  .draft-overview{max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;padding:120px 24px 72px}
  .draft-overview h1{font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3.1rem);line-height:1.05;color:var(--navy);margin:0 0 14px}
  .draft-overview p.lead{max-width:62ch;font-size:1rem;color:var(--slate);line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 26px}
  .draft-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));gap:var(--grid-gap-tight)}
  .draft-card{background:#fff;border:1px solid rgba(45,40,35,0.08);border-radius:var(--card-radius);padding:var(--card-padding);box-shadow:var(--card-shadow);display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:var(--grid-gap-tight)}
  .draft-badges{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .draft-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:var(--radius-pill);background:var(--green-bg);color:var(--navy);font-size:0.68rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase}
  .draft-badge.alert{background:#f6ddd5;color:var(--alert-red)}
  .draft-card h2{font-size:1.08rem;line-height:1.25;margin:0;color:var(--navy)}
  .draft-meta{font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--text-soft)}
  .draft-goal{font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.6;color:var(--slate);margin:0}
  .draft-links{display:flex;gap:var(--grid-gap-tight);flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:auto}
  .draft-link{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;min-height:40px;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:var(--radius-pill);text-decoration:none;font-size:0.82rem;font-weight:700}
  .draft-link.primary{background:var(--navy);color:#fff}
  .draft-link.secondary{background:#eef4f3;color:var(--navy)}
  @media(max-width:900px){.draft-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.draft-overview{padding-top:104px}}
</style>
{% endblock %}
{% block nav %}
{% include "nav-full.njk" %}
{% endblock %}
{% block content %}
<main class="draft-overview" id="main-content">
  <h1>Handout-Drafts</h1>
  <p class="lead">Diese Seite bündelt die neuen, wartbaren Voransichten für die priorisierten Handouts. Sie sind als redaktionelle und gestalterische Zwischenstufe gedacht, bevor daraus schlanke, neue PDFs exportiert werden.</p>

  <div class="draft-grid">
    {% for draft in collections.all | reverse %}
      {% if draft.url and draft.url.startsWith('/handout-drafts/') and draft.data.slug %}
      <article class="draft-card">
        <div class="draft-badges">
          <span class="draft-badge">{{ draft.data.priority }}</span>
          <span class="draft-badge{% if draft.data.type == 'Akutblatt' %} alert{% endif %}">{{ draft.data.type }}</span>
        </div>
        <h2>{{ draft.data.title }}</h2>
        <div class="draft-meta">{{ draft.data.target_format }} · Stand {{ draft.data.last_updated }}</div>
        <p class="draft-goal">{{ draft.data.goal }}</p>
        <div class="draft-links">
          <a class="draft-link primary" href="{{ draft.url }}">Draft öffnen</a>
          {% if draft.data.source_pdf %}<a class="draft-link secondary" href="{{ draft.data.source_pdf }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Altes PDF</a>{% endif %}
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</main>
{% endblock %}
